  ('customs-7fec267e-moex-00071', 'customs-7fec267e', 'customs-7fec267e-moex-113-6948958a', 'sub-customs-7fec267e-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '若總勞動生產函數（totalproductoflabor）為凹函數（concave），則下列敘述何者正確？', '["勞動平均生產力先遞增再遞減", "勞動平均生產力持續遞增", "勞動平均生產力持續遞減", "勞動平均生產力先遞減再遞增"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:22:21+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3fac22dc26b5", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8e5c03118776", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113040", "c": "142", "s": "0903", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學概要", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 13, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "customs", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('customs-7fec267e-moex-00072', 'customs-7fec267e', 'customs-7fec267e-moex-113-6948958a', 'sub-customs-7fec267e-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '某一廠商之生產函數為Q(K, L)=Min{aK, bL}，其中Q為產量、K與L分別為資本與勞動，係數a>0、 b>0，資本每單位價格為r，勞動每單位價格為w。當該廠商生產成本極小時，最適K/L比值為何？', '["b/a", "a/b", "w/r", "r/w"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:22:21+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3fac22dc26b5", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8e5c03118776", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113040", "c": "142", "s": "0903", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學概要", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 14, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "customs", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('customs-7fec267e-moex-00073', 'customs-7fec267e', 'customs-7fec267e-moex-113-6948958a', 'sub-customs-7fec267e-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '在完全競爭市場當中，假設市場的需求曲線為負斜率，如果所有廠商的平均成本皆下降10元，下列敘述 何者正確？', '["短期的市場均衡價格一定會下降10元", "短期的市場均衡價格一定會上升10元", "長期的市場均衡價格一定會下降10元", "長期的市場均衡價格一定會上升10元"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:22:21+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3fac22dc26b5", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8e5c03118776", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113040", "c": "142", "s": "0903", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學概要", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 15, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "customs", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
